GUBERNAMENTAL En comparaci\u00f3n con su participaci\u00f3n en el sector pesquero en general, las mujeres est\u00e1n sumamente subrepresentadas en los puestos de liderazgo corporativo y gubernamental.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "6f510a53-ec94-4f13-a0c6-85ebf83ede2b": {"__data__": {"id_": "6f510a53-ec94-4f13-a0c6-85ebf83ede2b", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/un-mar-de-oportunidades", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Un mar de oportunidades", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/un-mar-de-oportunidades", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "811fbbeaacb87d1afbe50c42e809abd92511ad5309f656e8cb628d6e8d382ad4"}, "2": {"node_id": "c4d22151-2e9b-424b-af8f-c7db8d3ad33d", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/un-mar-de-oportunidades", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "4e2bf7970ff9279fd53df83dac4f9fa9b243c71e0ac2ce7c5c8eaa338b5cfba5"}, "3": {"node_id": "fff4db12-b89e-49a1-8e9c-6e5198cf5afb", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/un-mar-de-oportunidades", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "e298ec7850e7cb74746513e073b113e56f826e073ee2f6f2ae3