ciones Unidas de lucha contra la desertificaci\u00f3n; d) Acuerdo de Paris; e) Contribuciones Nacionales Determinadas; f) Objetivos de Desarrollo Sostenible; g) Desaf\u00edo de Bonn; h) Declaraci\u00f3n de New York sobre los bosques, 2015 (Reducir a la mitad la p\u00e9rdida anual de bosques naturales para el 2020 y alcanzar la deforestaci\u00f3n 0 para el 2030)14.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "d2eabd0b-ccc6-4c44-98dd-082ad25c0c41": {"__data__": {"id_": "d2eabd0b-ccc6-4c44-98dd-082ad25c0c41", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/programa-nacional-de-conservacion-de-ecosistemas-terrestres-2021-2030", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Programa nacional de conservaci\u00f3n de ecosistemas terrestres 2021-2030", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/programa-nacional-de-conservacion-de-ecosistemas-terrestres-2021-2030", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "812b20dea8b07ec6f3e93d6e59820963b63e570871ef650380ceec62b45d039b"}, "2": {"node_id": "36fc16ba-4699-4804-a1a6-7e9e74f4248d", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/programa-nacional-de-conservacion-de-ecosistemas-terrestres-2021-2030", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "e494ea2de6c4eebe47e026ddae35e16776b2e4f2ad5fe3251a684be2730b5bc4"}}, "hash": "c081617a10fa4559